  </strong>If in the event there is a dispute on the cost the cost of such works shall  be evaluated and determined by either a judge from a court of law, independent  lawyer to both parties, or another party that both sides agree to.<br>
  <strong>5. RENOVATION /  CONSTRUCTION PROJECTS<br>
  </strong>Whist in our best efforts we always try to ensure that the product you are  paying for we have available in stock. However please note, if in the case we  are unable to supply you with the product you have purchased we will supply you  with the nearest equivalent as possible. Failing that we will refund you either  the difference, or the loss in full.<strong></strong><br>
