            <p><strong>6. PRICING STRUCTURE  / CONSULTANCY &amp; DESIGN COSTS <br>
              </strong>In most cases we do not charge additional costs for consultancy and design  of solutions for your applications. These Costs are reflected in our product  pricing already. In some cases we may state on the invoice directly the cost  for design and consultancy, if this price is not already taken into account  with our unit price for product. In some case you may feel our pricing to be  higher that is a direct result of the design and consultancy charge being  included into the product price. <br>
