            <p><strong>9. &nbsp;PURCHASE OF PRODUCTS AND DELIVERY<br>
            </strong>For first time orders under $10,000 Full payment must be made upon ordering  the products &amp; materials on discretion of NYTC International - NoiseStop  Systems Singapore for returning customers 50% deposit on order and the balance  to be paid in full on delivery.<strong></strong></p>
